summary: Celebrity Crush
title: Celebrity Crush
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2l7rEfA

by IMJGSEJK

Jimin and Yoongi are in LA for the summer to promote their new EP, and to make new connections for their future releases. The artist, and front figure is Jimin, and Yoongi produces for him. Jimins rise to fame happens faster than expected, and suddenly he is involved with his celebrity crush, the great Jeon Jungkook. He can’t believe it. But will his love be enough to change the, to the outside world straight, badboy heartthrob? Will Jungkook give anything up for Jimin or is it just an innocent flirt? And is it even worth it for Jimin himself? The newcomers in the industry are always the first ones to be forgotten. If he gets a bad reputation from the start he will be doomed. He can’t be like the others. Not when him and Yoongi worked so hard to be here.
